Münreader began as a personal necessity. As a lifelong reader, researcher, and ritual‑driven creator, I needed a device that honored the depth of reading without the noise of modern technology. No existing tool protected my focus, my data, or my creative rituals. So I built the device I could not find — a sanctuary in hardware form. Münreader exists because deep reading deserves a vessel worthy of it.

